ture, Tourism and Civil Aviation has decided to instruct the airlines to implement the PCR tests strictly.\n\nThe meeting also discussed formulating additional strategies to address the problems seen with the rise of coronavirus infection.\n\nSimilarly, various festivals, processions and other activities will be conducted as per the criteria set by the concerned district administration office, said Secretary Guragain.","title":"CCMC directs CDOs to ease coronavirus restrictions - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/03/124761/","video":[]}
